Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:35.02,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Adapted from novel of the same name, "The Grave Robbers' Chronicles (Dao Mu Bi Ji): Bronze Tree of Death" by Nanpai Sanshu\NOriginal work by Nanpai Sanshu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:38.60,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Chief Producer: Cheng Wu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:41.81,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Producer: Zou Zhengyu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:53.02,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(974,936)}The Grave Robbers' Chronicles  (Dao Mu Bi Ji): Bronze Tree of Death
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.85,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,An endless road ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:59.31,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Two extremities of love and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:04.02,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Inner demons shrouding the heart --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.44,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,they wallow in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.23,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where is my old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.31,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,He is lingering in the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:22.15,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Convinced that he hasn't veered too far off course, in this world of fleeting destinies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.77,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you pine? Why do you yearn?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:33.35,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Wishing to turn back, yet it was a path of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:37.60,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,The way of life is vicious, we keep going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.90,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Hard to discern truths from lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.98,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,to tell the evil from the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.48,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,In front of my eyes, a bungling mess of mountains and waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:50.15,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you tread a path this treacherous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:54.40,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Embroiled in sinister schemes, in trepidation as the tables turn and turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.85,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,I bid you adieu --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:00.56,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,shall we never meet again!
