Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.60,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Time has 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.69,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,drowned out even the claps of thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:22.52,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,They scatter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:26.48,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the cut-up pieces of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:32.35,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I can only fumble around, trying to piece them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:36.35,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why must I climb mountains and peaks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.15,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,to collect,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.10,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,but I seem to be late every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.15,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,tracks of hanging onto someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:50.98,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Those places I once trodden,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:55.15,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,how did they
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:59.10,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,look like originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:06.81,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Trying to trace those footsteps behind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.98,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I have forgotten;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:16.27,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the path I came from was too far and too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:22.27,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where would be the end of my journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.40,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:30.27,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:33.47,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where would it be...
